hopobject.body: Gloomy tales www.ehealth.com.cn I really can’t understand what is going on with so many gun murders. I hope the media does not become complacent to the commonness of these occurances. Sometimes, the story gets old and media seems to forget that there are actual victims out there. Gun violence in this country is carried out by people who hold up the constitution and then burn down a population of innocent people “Because they can.”
